OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FNew ad campaign to show    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fmortgage support           
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Lenders have launched a #5m advertising
OL,6, campaign to promote the support        
OL,7, available to mortgage holders if they  
OL,8, are struggling with repayments.        
OL,10,FThe help available includes extending  
OL,11,Fmortgage terms or switching to         
OL,12,Finterest-only repayments temporarily.  
OL,14,FThe move comes after bank bosses met   
OL,15,Fthe chancellor last month to discuss   
OL,16,Fways to help mortgage holders.         
OL,18,FThe campaign begins as new rules come  
OL,19,Finto force to improve standards for    
OL,20,Fpeople buying financial products.      
